---
title: Plant-Based Cheezy Kumara Burger with Spiced Fries & Burger Sauce
description: Welcome to a new world of veggie burgers. Instead of a meat patty, you’ll fry up a tasty kumara patty and plant-based cheese,
then pile it with crispy rocket leaves on a brioche-style bun. With a smear of our special burger sauce and fries on the side, this is
a burger for the record books!
